{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"665aa05ab9","title":"周恩来关于批判谭震林问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f15e2849cd","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":25,"articleId":"665aa05ab9","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"谭震林","id":"89f0012853","type":"人物"},{"name":"各级党政领导人","id":"a59dfa2519","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"da68fd0917","type":"title","text":"周恩来关于批判谭震林问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"665aa05ab9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1468e8ae9b","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十五日在天安门城楼上，周总理听完冯兴旺同学（北京农业大学革命委员会主任）汇报了农林口目前形势后，非常关心地说：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"665aa05ab9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f54ee54599","type":"paragraph","text":"我很关心农林口的问题，秦化龙的问题辩论很久了，但另一派不服气，我准备亲自参加一次辩论会，我已将秦的问题提交中央了，根据中央讨论结果，我准备把这个问题结束了。关于批谭，还是按前次提的方案，开个一千多人的会，会场我负责找，我说过了一定算数。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"665aa05ab9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94d3d9783e","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十九日周总理接见了农办农政双方代表，并作了指示：","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"665aa05ab9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"330687fc20","type":"paragraph","text":"秦化龙问题的辩论会不要再开了，不要因为秦化龙问题影响批判谭震林。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"665aa05ab9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"356f78b964","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理还指示，最近要把谭震林交给农林口革命造反派批、斗。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"665aa05ab9","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}